{"tid":882883,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲政府禁止中資企業建設5G網絡","createTime":"2018-10-30T11:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T19:06:17.000Z","uid":36551,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"017e24adcdb01b51a2de3ae9409753c2da639ee8","tid":882883,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"澳府首度解釋禁中資企業建5G網絡<br />\n2018/10/30 18:38<br />\n<br />\n澳洲政府早前禁止華為和中興通訊參與當地 5G 網絡建設，官方首次解釋，是要避免當地的基建受到威脅。 <br />\n<br />\n負責澳洲國防情報、網絡安全的信號局局長伯吉斯在一個晚宴上發言指，若有高風險的通訊設備遍及全澳洲的 5G 網絡，水電設施、醫療系統將不會受到足夠保護，屆時會很危險。政府在審慎考慮和諮詢專家意見後，決定禁止高危廠商參與 5G 網絡建設。<br />\n<br />\n華為早前已發信反駁，強調是獨立公司，有關威脅安全的說法是無根據。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/537225/即時新聞/澳府首度解釋禁中資企業建5G網絡\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F537225%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%BE%B3%E5%BA%9C%E9%A6%96%E5%BA%A6%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B%E7%A6%81%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%BB%BA5G%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1&d=bIkwlEUtBEDcqzqftKfRxJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=38461022\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F537225%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%BE%B3%E5%BA%9C%E9%A6%96%E5%BA%A6%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B%E7%A6%81%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%BB%BA5G%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1&h=285d6132\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/537225/即時新聞/澳府首度解釋禁中資企業建5G網絡</a>"},{"pid":"843f6c4eb8b7316f8bd764f2b18130fbd45e8765","tid":882883,"uid":65300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:57:16.000Z","msg":"做得好"},{"pid":"be84e9f163c16e9042ff0baba9ff6124945c05b7","tid":882883,"uid":7057,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T18:09:31.000Z","msg":"澳洲 美國禁 歐盟禁埋可以正式收皮，留返黎係非洲同一帶一路窮國鋪5G"},{"pid":"a458294a601ab5f49500c1deee264a86fa872bbf","tid":882883,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-1